   Ferris is a New American, seasonal restaurant from Charles Seich and
   Executive Chef Tyler Heckman

   . Located at 44 west 29th street, inside MADE, a new hotel in Nomad,
   the restaurant offers a dynamic 40-seat dining room with an open
   kitchen and seating at the chef's counter.

44 W 29TH ST NYC

212-213-4420
